
<item rdf:about='http://www.ietf.org/internet-drafts/draft-haas-xiao-bfd-echo-path-mtu-01.txt'>
    <title>"Application of the BFD Echo function for Path MTU Verification or Detection", Jeffrey Haas, Min Xiao</title>
    <link>http://www.ietf.org/internet-drafts/draft-haas-xiao-bfd-echo-path-mtu-01.txt</link>
    <description>This document specifies an extended application of the BFD Echo function for path MTU verification or detection, while preserving its original purpose for detecting forwarding failures.  This document defines a process to vary the length of some BFD Echo packets periodically to accomplish this Path MTU verification or detection.</description>
    <dc:date>2011-07-10T22:00:00-00:00</dc:date>
</item>
